                          "content": "da0 — 去中心化自治組織",
                          "fontFamily": "Noto Serif TC",
                          "fontSize": 32,
                          "fontWeight": "700"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "w9GnB",
                          "name": "oDesc",
                          "fill": "$--text-secondary",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "推動去中心化治理與公共財資助的台灣社群",
                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "rectangle",
                      "id": "ZBwPw",
                      "name": "oDivider",
                      "fill": "$--border",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "height": 1
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "vJtqK",
                      "name": "oBody",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 16,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "v2uqm",
                          "name": "oP1",
                          "fill": "$--text-primary",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "da0 是一個致力於推動去中心化自治的台灣社群。我們相信，透過區塊鏈技術和去中心化治理，可以建構更公平、更透明的公共財資助機制。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "i0wI3",
                          "name": "oH2",
                          "fill": "$--text-primary",
                          "content": "我們的使命",
                          "fontFamily": "Noto Serif TC",
                          "fontSize": 22,
                          "fontWeight": "700"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "vAB7d",
                          "name": "oP2",
                          "fill": "$--text-primary",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "da0 致力於降低公民參與公共事務的門檻，透過開源工具和教育資源，讓更多人能夠參與去中心化治理。我們的社群成員來自各個領域，包括工程師、設計師、研究者和公民倡議者。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "RBp14",
                          "name": "oH3",
