                          "name": "oP1",
                          "fill": "$--text-primary",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "da0 是一個致力於推動去中心化自治的台灣社群。我們相信，透過區塊鏈技術和去中心化治理，可以建構更公平、更透明的公共財資助機制。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "fjigT",
                          "name": "oH2",
                          "fill": "$--text-primary",
                          "content": "我們的使命",
                          "fontFamily": "Noto Serif TC",
                          "fontSize": 22,
                          "fontWeight": "700"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "ozMcq",
                          "name": "oP2",
                          "fill": "$--text-primary",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "da0 致力於降低公民參與公共事務的門檻，透過開源工具和教育資源，讓更多人能夠參與去中心化治理。我們的社群成員來自各個領域，包括工程師、設計師、研究者和公民倡議者。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
